{"tid":1448492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:46.000Z","uid":260269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"436dbbd97211e40bd443ab59c890d755c3ed8e1e","tid":1448492,"uid":260269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是他們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，是全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=f502de28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=2e393365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"80adde947dc80b9f23ca0881fd11ca63c2bdb2ce","tid":1448492,"uid":260269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ba3c12e38cb3a631d09f19c6159354974e26620b","tid":1448492,"uid":260269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"1faefa3198840c00a7521f190b909e2461350165","tid":1448492,"uid":260269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:58.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"72950ec03aa75e586b5d697bd5d0b7b27b1669f5","tid":1448492,"uid":260269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"267fd4d1284eec62ef3b98c9b16d825824b781e8","tid":1448492,"uid":2602